OL,3,CShop workers in 'fear of abuse and
OL,4,Cviolence' as thefts rise
OL,6,FUnion bosses have warned that retail
OL,7,Fstaff "are working in fear of abuse,
OL,8,Fthreats, or violence" as the amount of
OL,9,Fshoplifting incidents hits an all time
OL,10,Fhigh.
OL,12,FNearly 80% of retail staff in the
OL,13,FNorth West have suffered verbal abuse
OL,14,Fin the last year, and 7% were
OL,15,Fphysically assaulted.
OL,17,FThats according to retail union USDAW,
OL,18,Fit says that its deeply concerned
OL,19,Fabout the impact on its members.
