OL,3,CShop workers in 'fear of abuse and
OL,4,Cviolence' as thefts rise
OL,6,FThe British Retail Consortium has also
OL,7,Fpublished its annual crime report,
OL,8,Fwhich found a 50% increase in retail
OL,9,Fviolence and abuse, with more than
OL,10,F2,000 incidents a day in 2024. The
OL,11,Freport found that shoplifting cost the
OL,12,Fretail industry #2.2 billion in 2023/
OL,13,F24, despite shop owners spending #1.8
OL,14,Fbillion on prevention methods.
OL,16,FUsdaw general secretary Paddy Illis
OL,17,Fsays: "The scale of the epidemic of
OL,18,Fretail crime is laid bare in these
OL,19,Fshocking police recorded crime
OL,20,Fstatistics and the BRC report.
