OL,3,CShop workers in 'fear of abuse and
OL,4,Cviolence' as thefts rise
OL,6,F"Crime has a very direct impact on the
OL,7,Fviability of stores, as retailers go
OL,8,Fto increasing lengths and expense to
OL,9,Fmake them secure and safe.
OL,11,F"Staff are working in fear of the next
OL,12,Fincident of abuse, threats or
OL,13,Fviolence."
OL,15,FUsdaw warns organised crime gangs
OL,16,Facross the North West are targeting
OL,17,Fshops and threatening staff with
OL,18,Fweapons and violence, causing huge
OL,19,Ffinancial losses and distress to
OL,20,Fworkers.
