OL,3,CShop workers in 'fear of abuse and
OL,4,Cviolence' as thefts rise
OL,6,FPaddy said: "Having to deal with
OL,7,Frepeated and persistent offences can
OL,8,Fcause issues beyond the theft itself,
OL,9,Flike anxiety, fear and physical harm
OL,10,Fto retail workers."
OL,12,FUsdaw has been campaigning with the
OL,13,FBritish Retail Consortium to tackle
OL,14,Fthe rise in shoplifting, and say they
OL,15,Fare "pleased to see the Government
OL,16,Fwill be introducing... measures to
OL,17,Ftackle the issue."
