OL,3,CShop workers in 'fear of abuse and
OL,4,Cviolence' as thefts rise
OL,6,FThe Crime and Policing Bill is
OL,7,Fcurrently making its way through
OL,8,FParliament, and will end the current
OL,9,Fpractice of only prosecuting
OL,10,Fshoplifters who steal more than #200
OL,11,Fworth of goods.
OL,13,FUsdaw says this rule acts as an "open
OL,14,Finvitation to retail criminals" to
OL,15,Fstill little and often.
OL,17,FPaddy said: "It is our hope that these
OL,18,Fnew measures will help give retail
OL,19,Fworkers the respect they deserve."
